description: Extension of Atlip Road and erection of four buildings containing 5 commercial units (733 square metres) and 186 flats comprising 60 one- and two-bedroom private flats and 126 one-, two-, three- and four-bedroom affordable flats.  The buildings on the northwest side of the access road are 4-storey and part 4- and 6-storey. The buildings on the southeast side are part 8- and 9-storey and part 10- and 14-storey.  Provision of 54 car-parking spaces, cycle parking, refuse storage, landscaping, 2 children's play areas and footbridge over the canal
